ag-prayer-al-salat","tag-recommendation-al-mustahab","tag-voluntary-prayers-salat-nafilah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-7k0","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":28121,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/ten-rakaat-sunan\/","url_meta":{"origin":28148,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary Sunan prayers throughout day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I prayed with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, two prostrations before and after noon prayer, two prostrations after sunset prayer, two prostrations after evening prayer, and two prostrations after Friday prayer. As for sunset and evening prayer, they were in his house. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12964,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/four-sunan-rakaat-after-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":28148,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jumuah: Four Sunan cycles after Friday prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"When one of you performs Friday prayer, let him pray four cycles\u00a0after it.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 881 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u06